==Bosnian==
===Proper noun===
'''Srbijanac''' ''m s''
#a [[Serb]], a citizen of [[Serbia]] (not necessarily of [[Serb]] ethnicity). The term is considered to be slightly derogatory; the adjectiv [[Serbian]] or a noun [[Serb]] should be used instead (Eg. She is Serbian, or She is a Serb). 
